ass=\"js-video [vimeo, widescreen] active\">\n<iframe frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/236941713\"></iframe>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-isolate-scope ui-sortable ng-not-empty\"><li id=\"VSe5M\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed selected-class   ui-resizable\" style=\"position: relative; left: 0px; top: 0px;\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None ng-touched\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5>Lesson Summary</h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"l3N5x\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None background\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5>The main points from this module are as follows:</h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"OaIBg\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list list-item, listed ui-resizable   border\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" class=\"list-item editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty fontNormal None ng-touched\"><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"\"><b>The Federal Reserve</b> is considered a powerful institution because it has the power to buy government bonds, act as a lender of last resort, and create money.</li><li class=\"\">The Federal Reserve can control short-run growth better than long-term growth but even then, there are limits to its powers to influence short-term growth, in part because it has incomplete data about the economy, lagged results from policy to growth, and limited control.<br></li><li class=\"\">The <b>monetary base</b> is best described as currency plus reserve deposits.<br></li><li class=\"\">Banks are allowed to loan out up to 90%, a practice known as fractional reserve banking.<br></li><li class=\"\">The Federal Deposit Insurance Corporation <b>(FDIC)</b> insures deposit accounts.<br></li><li class=\"\">When the government increases taxes on corporations, this is called contractionary fiscal policy.<br></li><li class=\"\">Cheap credit can stimulate aggregate demand.<br></li></ul></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li></ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-isolate-scope ui-sortable ng-not-empty\"><li id=\"vCbQ5\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed selected-class   border ui-resizable\" style=\"position: relative; left: 0px; top: 0px;\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None ng-touched\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5>Learning Outcomes</h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"nj5qp\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None background\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5>Upon completion of this module, you will be able to:</h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"BRk6F\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list list-item, listed ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" class=\"list-item editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty fontNormal None\"><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"\">Explain fiscal policy.</li><li class=\"\">Discuss the purpose of expansionary fiscal policy.&nbsp;<br></li><li class=\"\">Describe an ideal stimulus.<br></li><li class=\"\">Discuss the dangers of fiscal policy.<br></li></ul></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li></ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ui-sortable ng-not-empty\">\n<li id=\"GGMWL\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed\">\n<div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-not-empty None background\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5>Introduction to Fiscal Policy</h5></div>\n<div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div>\n</li><li id=\"O0eoZ\" data-space=\"video\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list active, listed selected-class video-box\">\n<div class=\"video-edit editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-not-empty None\">\n<div class=\"video-content\" style=\"display: none;\">\n<p>Select your Video URL in the Edit Panel</p>\n<span class=\"icon-video\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"js-video [vimeo, widescreen] active\">\n<iframe frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/236944100\"></iframe>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ui-sortable ng-not-empty\">\n<li id=\"JDVSo\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed   ui-resizable\">\n<div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-not-empty None background\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5>Fiscal Policy: The Best Case Scenario</h5></div>\n<div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div>\n</li><li id=\"cSOWN\" data-space=\"video\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list active, listed selected-class video-box\">\n<div class=\"video-edit editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-not-empty None\">\n<div class=\"video-content\" style=\"display: none;\">\n<p>Select your Video URL in the Edit Panel</p>\n<span class=\"icon-video\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"js-video [vimeo, widescreen] active\">\n<iframe frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/236944206\"></iframe>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ui-sortable ng-not-empty\">\n<li id=\"zq7H1\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed\">\n<div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-not-empty None background\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5>The Limits of Fiscal Policy</h5></div>\n<div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div>\n</li><li id=\"GaRoj\" data-space=\"video\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list active, listed selected-class video-box\">\n<div class=\"video-edit editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-not-empty None\">\n<div class=\"video-content\" style=\"display: none;\">\n<p>Select your Video URL in the Edit Panel</p>\n<span class=\"icon-video\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"js-video [vimeo, widescreen] active\">\n<iframe frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/236944313\"></iframe>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-isolate-scope ui-sortable ng-not-empty\"><li id=\"qNeRk\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed selected-class   border ui-resizable\" style=\"position: relative; left: 0px; top: 0px;\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None ng-touched\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5>Lesson Summary</h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"n27VF\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None background\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5>The main points from this module are as follows:</h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"Q8o4J\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list list-item, listed ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" class=\"list-item editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty fontNormal None ng-touched\"><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"\"><b>Fiscal policy </b>is a government’s policies on taxes, spending, and borrowing.</li><li class=\"\">Fiscal policy can be used to mitigate fluctuations in the business cycle.<br></li><li class=\"\"><b>Expansionary fiscal policy</b> refers to when the government increases spending to put unemployed workers to work. Because workers will be earning money, they’ll spend money. The recipients of that spending will spend more, and so on. This is the “fiscal multiplier”.<br></li><li class=\"\">An <b>ideal stimulus</b> is: timely, targeted, and temporary.<br></li><li class=\"\">Timeliness refers to how quickly the government can recognize a recession and apply a solution. Because this can take quite a while, automatic stabilizers can be more effective. This can include progressive tax codes or unemployment insurance.<br></li><li class=\"\"><b>Government spending</b> can give the economy a short-run boost. However, debt-financed spending can accrue a lot of interest.<br></li></ul></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li></ul>\n"]}